item.title: Introduction
item.description:
Greeting!

I have experience working with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Databases, PHP and Linux for web applications and networking security projects. My interests include ethical hacking, server administration, and secure web development. I’m passionate about technology, cybersecurity, and innovation, always looking to expand my knowledge and work on challenging projects.

Let’s connect and collaborate!
